{
  "texts": [
    "These results demonstrate a very high degree of agreement with our expectations.",
    "The experts also stated that the McRE framework is suitable for multicultural requirements elicitation not only in software projects but also in other domains.",
    "Tables 5 to 14 also show the three most prevalent comments/opinions provided by the experts.",
    "Finally, the tables show the critical opinions, drawbacks/hurdles as well as the experts' suggestions.",
    "Every table presents the comments of the experts in their own words (shown in italics)."
  ]
}